txt.en: You should return to Candúr and inform him of your deeds within The Towers of the Teeth.

Those who dwell in The Towers of the Teeth are numerous. Driving off even a fraction of their number will better position the Host of the West to travel safety through The Wastes.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Towers of the Teeth: Guardian of the Teeth to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
'You have done well, friend. Your efforts will be duly noted!'

Defeat Black Númenóreans in The Towers of the Teeth
Defeat Black Númenóreans within The Towers of the Teeth.
To weaken the resolve of the invaders within The Towers of the Teeth, you take it upon yourself to thin their numbers.
